        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">Learn about our journey, values, and commitment to excellence</p>
      </section>

      <!-- About Section -->
      <section class="handyman-section">
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Our Story</h2>
          
          <p>Founded in 2010, John's Professional Handyman Services began with a simple mission: to provide reliable, high-quality home repair and improvement services at fair prices. What started as a one-person operation has grown into a trusted name in our community, known for exceptional craftsmanship and customer service.</p>
          
          <p>Over the past decade, we've completed thousands of projects, from minor repairs to major renovations, always maintaining our commitment to excellence. Our reputation has been built on word-of-mouth recommendations from satisfied customers, and we continue to take pride in every job we complete.</p>
          
          <div class="stats">
            <div class="stat-box">
              <h3 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin: 0;">10+</h3>
              <p>Years Experience</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
              <h3 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin: 0;">2500+</h3>
              <p>Projects Completed</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
              <h3 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin: 0;">98%</h3>
              <p>Client Satisfaction</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
              <h3 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin: 0;">4.9</h3>
              <p>Avg. Rating</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

