            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150x150/3498db/ffffff?text=John+D." alt="John Doe" class="team-photo">
            <div>
              <h3>John Doe - Owner & Lead Technician</h3>
              <p>With over 15 years of hands-on experience in residential and commercial repairs, John brings expertise in plumbing, electrical work, carpentry, and general maintenance. He personally oversees every project to ensure the highest quality standards.</p>
              <p>Certifications: Licensed Plumber, Electrical Safety Certified, OSHA Safety Trained</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="team-member">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150x150/e74c3c/ffffff?text=Mike+S." alt="Mike Smith" class="team-photo">
            <div>
              <h3>Mike Smith - Senior Carpenter</h3>
              <p>Mike specializes in carpentry, finish work, and custom installations. With 12 years of experience, he excels at creating beautiful and functional solutions for our clients' needs.</p>
              <p>Certifications: Certified Carpenter, Woodworking Specialist</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Values Section -->
      <section class="handyman-section">
        <div style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
          <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Our Core Values</h2>
          
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px;">
              <h3>Quality Craftsmanship</h3>
              <p>We never cut corners and always use the best materials and techniques to ensure lasting results.</p>
